{"tid":864532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[多撚謝] 港鐵「擇日」提供一天半價優惠","createTime":"2018-10-16T09:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T10:42:10.000Z","uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6c011d487aa5a9d3ca0211ae9cc6d6e9015228a2","tid":864532,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/00d/183/00d1835d432c7ebc68735b47c8bc1fdd229589ac_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F00d%2F183%2F00d1835d432c7ebc68735b47c8bc1fdd229589ac_b.jpg&h=f5c1ca5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵今早港島、觀塘、荃灣、將軍澳共4線先後發生信號故障，至中午前才全線恢復正常服務，全港交通大混亂，不少市民上班上學行程嚴重延誤。港鐵常務總監金澤培表示，為感謝乘客一直以來的支持及今日的體諒，將盡快找一天提供半價乘車優惠，詳情稍後公布。<br />\n<br />\n金澤培表示，港鐵非常關注今次事件，將成立委員會調查事故，且由於這次事故較獨特、技術性較重，所以將邀請外來信號系統專家找出原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181016/s00001/1539679733723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181016%2Fs00001%2F1539679733723&d=19R18GhNToue5Ck1nXThuzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=77c5452e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181016%2Fs00001%2F1539679733723&h=0f39eeee\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181016/s00001/1539679733723</a>"},{"pid":"9d4b7b34f95c2f32599d88ec6aba2ed3b358cf5c","tid":864532,"uid":83914,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:25:35.000Z","msg":"累你勤工獎500$無左。還番10$車費俾你"},{"pid":"f6651c2fea0d0f605b9b66f36a5cb51c50704e5b","tid":864532,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由於這次事故較獨特、技術性較重，所以將邀請外來信號系統專家<span style=\"color: red;\">找出原因</span>。</blockquote><br />\n啫係自己都唔知衰乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌晒港鐵啲人嘅老母<